<!-- ═══ STORY SECTION ═══ -->
<section class="about section-padding">
  <div class="blueprint-grid"></div>
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-text">
      <div class="section-label reveal">01 &mdash; Our Story</div>
      <h2 class="section-heading reveal">Built on Belief</h2>
      <p class="reveal reveal-d1">Founded by Gerard Albert in 2014, Albertium began with a conviction that architecture should serve both people and the planet. From a small studio in London, we set out to prove that sustainability and striking design are not opposites &mdash; they are partners.</p>
      <p class="reveal reveal-d2">A decade later, that philosophy has guided over 300 projects across residential, commercial, and cultural sectors. Every line we draw is informed by context, every material chosen with purpose, and every space designed to elevate the daily experience of those who use it.</p>
      <div class="founder-tag reveal reveal-d3">
        <span>Gerard Albert</span> &mdash; Founder &amp; Principal Architect
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-visual reveal">
      <div class="about-visual-placeholder clip-reveal"></div>
      <div class="about-img-overlay"></div>
      <div class="about-img-line"></div>
